brazil make second amazon oil discoveri the brazilian state oil compani petrobra ha made a second oil discoveri in the amazon region , presid jose sarney said . he said the well had an initi flow of 150,000 cubic meter of ga and 220 barrel of oil per day . it is situat 14 kilometr from the first well to be discov in the region last year , which is current yield 500,000 cubic meter of ga and 900 barrel of oil daili . the well , the biggest onshor well in the countri , are on the bank of the river uruc in the amazon basin 3,600 kilometr ( 2,250 mile ) north of brasilia .